{"tid":111143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年假後兩學童自殺亡 父母不能說的「禁話」","createTime":"2017-02-07T08:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T10:46:39.000Z","uid":65710,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6677517702f49345d1f09e468d225e7eb166a8","tid":111143,"uid":65710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"農曆新年假期結束後開學日，即有兩名學童自殺身亡。今晨6時許，一名穿校服及黑鞋的女學生於青衣長康邨康祥樓從高處墮下，女生被緊急送院搶救後證實不治。另外，一名16歲中四男學生昨晨9時多亦於馬鞍山墮樓亡，救護員接報到場，惟搶救亦同樣宣告不治。警方其後始證實男死者姓羅（16歲），警方正調查其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n時下香港學生讀書壓力大，作為家長或同輩，請緊記給學生多點關愛。然而，聖公會聖匠堂安寧服務部高級服務經理梁梓敦則提醒大家，安慰說話不可隨便說，否則隨時講多錯多。<br />\n<br />\n梁梓敦表示，綜合過往組織處理的個案分析，不少人在聽到朋友向他們表達「我想死」的念頭時，感到害怕之餘，又不知如何適當地回應對方，只懂不停勸對方「不要死」，惟始終未能了解傾訴者的內心感受，解決傾訴者欲尋死的原因，一句隨口回應，不能安撫心靈，隨時適得其反。<br />\n<br />\n聖公會聖匠堂安寧服務部的DEATHFEST，在社交媒體貼文，提醒各人在關懷身邊受情緒困擾的朋友時，回應宜尊重傾訴者的獨立性及個人經歷，忌給予過多批評式及埋怨式回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dav0ftup\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdav0ftup&h=0e62980b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁梓敦解釋，「你會對唔住父母架」，這話會加重對方的內疚及自殺感，忌將估計的想法用作安慰說話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u21agykl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu21agykl&h=cfb0fa73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁梓敦提醒，「你咪成日唔開心啦」，這句話會令對方覺得你在埋怨或反駁他，從而令對方感傷心不獲認同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h67jnfqk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh67jnfqk&h=5dd6f41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梓敦說，「香港地個個都係咁啦」只是淡化對方感覺，應表示理解對方的不開心是獨特的，信任對方可走出困境，例如說：''人人都有煩惱，但我估你，一定好辛苦。''<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0cq86s2p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0cq86s2p&h=a177cdba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁梓敦說，「唔好諗咁多啦」只會終結對話，令對方認為你沒有耐性聽下去，索性不談。<br />\n''我可唔可以聽你講多少少』是將心比己，鼓勵對方繼續表達。''<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSAD BUT TURE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[ur]<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1655477/%E5%B9%B4%E5%81%87%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%A1%20%20%20%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%AA%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%81%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%8D[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1655477%2F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2581%2587%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A1%2520%2520%2520%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E7%259A%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%258D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=43836ec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1655477/%E5%B9%B4%E5%81%87%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%A1%20%20%20%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%AA%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%81%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%8D[/url]</a>"},{"pid":"4b59c513d95af882e9f34809d3088e7d23f51715","tid":111143,"uid":65710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1655477/%E5%B9%B4%E5%81%87%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%A1%20%20%20%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%AA%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%81%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1655477%2F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2581%2587%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A1%2520%2520%2520%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E7%259A%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%258D&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4a252c14\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1655477/%E5%B9%B4%E5%81%87%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%A1%20%20%20%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%AA%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%81%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%8D</a>[/quote]"},{"pi